\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
After some algebraic manipulations we arrive at:
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $=\sqrt{\frac{i\hbar}{2\pi m}}\left(t_{b}-t_{a}\right)^{-\frac{3}{2}}\left(t_{b}-t_{1}\right)\left(t_{2}-t_{a}\right)$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\blacksquare$
